Package: localmap
Title: Local Species Occurrence Mapping Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Barry", family = "Brook", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: Tools for sourcing, harmonising, and mapping species occurrence data
    managed by the Localmap project. The compendium keeps the reproducible
    workflow conventions from the template, integrating 'renv', 'targets', and
    'Quarto' to support transparent biodiversity analyses.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.5)
